  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220667525309\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220667525309\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">자동차 보험으로 치료받으시는분이 이수한의원에&nbsp;오셨다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">일때문에 많이 바쁘신지 일주일 1~2번정도 내원하신다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘은 손에 무언가를 들고오셨다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;나: \"안녕하세요~\"</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">환자분: \"네 안녕하세요.. 저 이거...\"</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">다름아닌 시원한 음료였다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160328_284/isuhani_1459137461460Y1l9Q_JPEG/P3285248.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"400\" height=\"300\" style=\"cursor: pointer; line-height: 1.5; rheight: 300px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20160328_284/isuhani_1459137461460Y1l9Q_JPEG/P3285248.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360CF38BD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160328_284/isuhani_1459137461460Y1l9Q_JPEG/P3285248.JPG?type=w3\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">아이스티인줄 알았다&nbsp;</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/30f36ff4e119880d.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"533\" style=\"cursor: pointer; line-height: 1.5; rheight: 533px; rwidth: 400px;\" id=\"20160328_264/isuhani_1459137461761qQUAV_JPEG/P3285249.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003360CF38BD')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/30f36ff4e119880d.jpg\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">한모금 쭉 빨았는데</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">또르르... 아이스커피였다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋ</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">안그래도 목이 마르는거같아서 물을 마실까 말까 하고있었는데</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">때마침 환자분께서 시원한 음료수로 주셔서</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있게 잘마셨다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅎㅎ</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0c4f41b80b8cfc57.png\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-23\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">잘마셨습니다^^</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&#8203;</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&#8203;</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>&#8203;</span></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이수한의원 전체가 시원해진 듯 하다</div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></div><p>&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
